headline: Q3 Earnings Roundup: Carrier Global (NYSE:CARR) And The Rest Of The HVAC and Water Systems Segment
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at hvac and water systems stocks, starting with Carrier Global (NYSE:CARR).
